Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, aren't you Emi Honma,\Nthe teenage idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see your picture in the magazines.\N-I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say if it puts\Nsomeone in a difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to tell you.\NThe truth is, I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been dating someone, but no one,\Nnot even my management agency, knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I put a picture\Ntaken of us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...in my locket\Nand always kept it near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, when I left it in\Nmy dressing room for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mr. Iwasaki from a rival\Nproduction came and stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Mr. Iwasaki came\Nto me and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see, what should I do\Nabout this, this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The press would go crazy\Nif I sold it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would mean\Nthe end of your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please, give it back to me!\N-OK, I'll give it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, your part\Nas Yoko in that new movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...you could turn down the part\Nand give it to one of my girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You could pretend to be sick\Nor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do it, I won't be\Nresponsible for this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause trouble\Nfor my agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here because\NI don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please cheer up.\NI'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,SAVE THE PRETTY IDOL GIRL!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Big news, big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The shampoo company's\Nimage girl contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you passed\Nthe preliminaries! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, you're one step closer\Nto becoming a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is great!\N-You'll go to the contest, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you become a big star,\Ndon't forget about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! She'll be so busy, she won't\Neven be able to come to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, wow!\N-Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think becoming a big star\Nis that easy, you're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's with him? Spoilsport.\N-Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, was it something we said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.\NRina also passed. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure she entered herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a lot\Nof confidence in herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to participate\Nin the contest! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Meimi, listen. That girl Emi\Nwho came here yesterday for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who wants her locket?\NI'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand. Emi is one\Nof the judges for that contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She was one of the past winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Mr. Iwasaki is\Nalso one of the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless Emi announces she is turning\Ndown the role by that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...he says he'll publicize the picture\Nafter the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think our best bet would be\Nto get the locket...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...during the contest\Nand return it to Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But why do I have to enter a contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never have guessed that\Nyou were so afraid of contests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just hold on there!\N-Forget it. Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says I'm afraid? All right then,\NI'll show you. I'll enter that contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A note!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"On the day of the beauty contest,\NI'll take a locket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...from Mr. Iwasaki of the Rainbow\NProduction Company. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear?\NI'm entering that contest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to test my capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one Sawatari was talking about,\Nyou're in it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come and watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go?\NGirls are a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right. Now give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you think about, St. Tail!\NIt was a man dressed like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a future star\Nstanding right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., have you, you know,\Ngotten taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better make my move. Soon the\Nother girls will start noticing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better stake my claim on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi there!\N- Hi, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Emi Honma's being interviewed on TV.\N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi, congratulations\Non getting the role of Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NI owe everything to all my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And does that include your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My boyfriend is all of my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Emi, it must be hard for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. She's too young\Nto have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even junior high kids have\Nsignificant others these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, you don't have a boyfriend,\Ndo you? You're much too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined!\NMy Meimi's got a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, my idyllic life\Nis coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, dear. Meimi hasn't said\Nanything about liking a certain boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't like boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you prefer girls?\NThat is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a heart-to-heart talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Enough of this nonsense!\N-But, Eimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Ruby. Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my best friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I had something on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I become a star,\NI wonder if he'll look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Yamashiro.\NI'm in charge of this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Iwasaki\Nfrom Rainbow Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better arrest that burglar.\NShe's such a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father may be a detective,\Nbut how will you arrest her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from this building's floor\Nplan and her mode of operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's a high possibility\Nshe'll appear directly on-stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I thought we could rig\Nthe stage curtain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...to fall on her like a casting net,\Nthus trapping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. You have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will capture her.\NI won't fail this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the contest begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,First is a question-and-answer\Nsegment, then a camera test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry 1, please come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry 1, Manami Yoshizawa.\NI'm 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you currently most devoted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To my music and dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am also serious about putting\Nevery effort into this audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are your dreams for the future?\N-To become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please turn to the right.\N-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now turn around and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a complete turn.\NThat's fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-This isn't easy, is it?\N-Next contestant, entry 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Mutsumi Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Yoko Hizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Yuki Uchida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira, where's Rina and Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sure they'll be out soon.\N-I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Rina Takamiya.\NI'm 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,15, is there someone special\Nin your life now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, smile.\NNow turn to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn that St. Tail. Why does she\Nwant the locket Mr. Iwasaki has?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. I've got to concentrate\Non capturing her, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, come on, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 18.\NMy name is Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I'm 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your idea of the perfect man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This I've got to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I think I goofed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that concludes\Nour program for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The results of today's judging\Nof these 50 contestants...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be sent out within 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still one left, 51!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This part of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is there someone left?\N-No, I'm sure there were only 50 girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the lights!\NWhere are the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, I pray God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, drop the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better not move around now.\NBesides, you seem pretty slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll be safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?\NI haven't told any jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the curtain! Hurry!\NWhat's the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Asuka Jr.! We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 51, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a thief! How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! You're not getting the locket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you, Mr. Iwasaki!\NYou won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Beauty contests are fun\Nbut how's this shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the locket!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn this smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going\Nto get that St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed.\NAs the mayor's niece, I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats. You're not\Ngetting away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who does it,\Njust pull the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Asuka Jr.!\N-Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. I've got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't exactly going as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- This can't be happening!\N-I've got you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.! Sorry! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't arrest her!\NShe got my locket back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She got my locket back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sure bet that I didn't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never tell! Sometimes\Nthey go for things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Seira.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NYou had the best response!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I goofed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up, trying to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father wouldn't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were your father, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disappointment!\NBoth Meimi and Rina didn't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought they'd be able to\Nintroduce us to some handsome actors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive\Nhe had her trapped back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But he let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a great idea.\NI'll keep St. Tail away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, he's sure to notice me!
